Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> calc
Rule 1     calc -> exp next
Rule 2     exp -> NAME OP exp CP
Rule 3     exp -> exp more
Rule 4     exp -> NAME
Rule 5     more -> COMA exp more
Rule 6     more -> COMA exp
Rule 7     next -> DOUBLESEMICOLON
Rule 8     next -> DOUBLESEMICOLON calc

Terminals, with rules where they appear

COMA                 : 5 6
CP                   : 2
DOUBLESEMICOLON      : 7 8
NAME                 : 2 4
OP                   : 2
error                : 

Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

calc                 : 8 0
exp                  : 1 2 3 5 6
more                 : 3 5
next                 : 1

Parsing method: LALR

